value.title: Biden, Harris partake in Arlington wreath laying ceremony
value.excerpt: President Joe Biden and Vice President Kamala Harris, after being sworn in at the Capitol, traveled to Arlington National Cemetery for a ceremony at the Tomb of the Unknown Soldier.

value.title: Sotomayor mispronounces Kamala Harris' name – Twitter reacts
